{"title_page": "Cyber Security & Crime Division, CTTC, DMP", "text_new": "{{short description|Branch of Bangladesh Police}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox law enforcement agency\n|agencyname     = Cyber Security & Crime Division \n|police         = Yes\n|headquarters   = 36 Minto Road, Ramna, [[Dhaka]] 1217\n|parentagency   = [[Dhaka Metropolitan Police]]\n|country        = Bangladesh\n|chief1name     = A F M Al Kibria\n|chief1position = Deputy Commissioner\n|employees      = 100\n|formedmonthday = 3 May\n|formedyear     = 2016\n|website        = {{URL|cttcdmp.gov.bd}}\n}}The '''Cyber Security & Crime Division''', more commonly known as the Cyber Crime Unit,<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/news/11220/dmps-counter-terrorism-unit-headed-by-monirul|title=DMP's counter-terrorism unit headed by Monirul|last=|first=|date=2016-02-18|work=Daily Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.observerbd.com/details.php?id=75128|title=DMP set to purchase 15 types of \u2018cyber arms\u2019|last=|first=|date=2017-05-24|work=The Daily Observer|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/bangladesh-news/those-spreading-rape-victims-photos-on-social-media-to-face-action-dmp/43065|title=Those spreading rape victims\u2019 photos on social media to face action: DMP|last=|first=|date=2017-05-20|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://en.banglatribune.com/others/news/43701/Investigation-into-Gulistan%E2%80%99s-bomb-underway-DMP|title=Investigation into Gulistan\u2019s bomb underway: DMP chief|last=|first=|date=2019-04-30|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> is a branch of [[Bangladesh Police]] which is operated under the [[Counter Terrorism and Transnational Crime]] of [[Dhaka Metropolitan Police]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/backpage/cybercrime-the-rise-1579035|title=Cybercrime on the rise|last=Islam, Jamil Khan|first=Shariful, Mohammad|date=2018-05-21|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/crime/2017/10/01/militants-secured-apps-dodge-cops|title=Militants using secured messaging apps to dodge cops|last=Mahmud, Rahman Rabbi|first=Tarek, Arifur|date=2017-10-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dmp.gov.bd/counter-terrorism/|title=Counter Terrorism|last=|first=|date=2018-12-01|website=Dhaka Metropolitan Police|location=Dhaka|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref> The main function of this division is to patrol, prevent, detect and investigate [[Cyberterrorism|cyber-terrorism]] and [[Cybercrime|cyber-crime]] in [[Dhaka|Dhaka Metropolitan]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/backpage/cybercrime-the-rise-1579035|title=Cybercrime on the rise|last=Islam, Jamil Khan|first=Shariful, Mohammad|date=2018-05-18|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/special-news/Concerns-growing-over-sexual-harassment-of-girls-on-social-media%C2%A0/71670|title=Concerns growing over sexual harassment of girls on social media|last=Shithi|first=Wahida Zaman|date=2018-05-27|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/showtime/2019/02/12/miss-world-bangladesh-2017-jessia-files-complaint-over-cyberbullying|title=Miss World Bangladesh 2017 Jessia files complaint over cyberbullying|last=|first=|date=2019-02-12|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/01/rise-in-cybercrime-worries-women|title=Rise in cybercrime worries women|last=|first=|date=2019-04-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/21/over-900-cases-related-to-cybercrimes-filed-in-2018|title=Over 900 cases related to cybercrimes filed in 2018|last=Islam Tipu|first=Md Sanul|date=2019-04-21|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/@pathao_ltd/cyber-security-crime-division-cttc-dmps-report-regarding-pathao-44a7e8db4fee|title=Cyber Security & Crime Division, CTTC, DMP\u2019s Report Regarding Pathao|last=|first=|date=2018-11-13|website=Medium|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-13}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\nThis division commenced its operation on 3 May 2016.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/114536/DMP-launches-counterterrorism-unit|title=DMP launches counter-terrorism unit|last=|first=|date=2016-02-16|work=Daily Sun|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/print-news/7856|title=DMP's counterterrorism unit likely from Feb -The Asian Age|last=|first=|date=2016-01-01|work=Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.clickittefaq.com/dmps-special-counter-terrorism-unit-to-start-functioning-in-february/|title=DMP\u2019s special counter terrorism unit to start functioning in February|last=|first=|date=2016-02-15|work=Ittefaq|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> Amidst the rise of [[Cybercrime|cyber crimes]] and [[Cyberbullying|cyber bullying]] in [[Bangladesh]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/post/194198|title=Cybercrimes escalate worries to female internet users|last=|first=|date=2019-04-02|work=The Independent BD|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/380753/2019/03/28/40-cases-filed-with-DMP-every-day|title=40 cases filed with DMP every day|last=Salman|first=Md Solaiman|date=2019-03-19|work=Daily Sun|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/01/rise-in-cybercrime-worries-women|title=Rise in cybercrime worries women|last=|first=|date=2019-04-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://en.banglatribune.com/tech-and-gadget/news/35788/Cyber-crime-committed-every-twenty-seconds|title=Cyber-crime committed every twenty seconds|last=Sarwar|first=Dipu|date=2019-03-25|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref> the policy makers took initiative to launch this dedicated Cyber Crime Division for Dhaka Metropolitan that will address digital crimes including [[Cyberbullying|online harassment]], [[Security hacker|hacking]], [[Internet fraud|Financial Fraud Crime]] and many more.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.observerbd.com/details.php?id=75128|title=DMP set to purchase 15 types of \u2018cyber arms\u2019|last=|first=|date=2017-05-24|work=The Daily Observer|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.clickittefaq.com/dmps-special-counter-terrorism-unit-to-start-functioning-in-february/|title=DMP\u2019s special counter terrorism unit to start functioning in February|last=|first=|date=2016-01-15|work=Ittefaq|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref>\n\n== Vision ==\nProtecting the [[netizen]]s of Dhaka Metropolitan by preventing cyber crime.\n\n== Mission ==\n<mapframe latitude=\"23.744\" longitude=\"90.404\" zoom=\"15\" width=\"263\" height=\"100\" align=\"right\" />[[File:Cyber Crime Unit, CTTC, DMP.jpg|thumb|''Cyber Division Help Desk''|alt=|262x262px]]\nKeeping the netizens of Dhaka Metropolitan safe and secured by investigating cyber incidents; monitoring social media sites, blogs and by raising public awareness.\n\n== Organization ==\nHeadquartered in 36 Minto Road, Ramna, [[Dhaka]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/showtime/2019/02/12/miss-world-bangladesh-2017-jessia-files-complaint-over-cyberbullying|title=Miss World Bangladesh 2017 Jessia files complaint over cyberbullying|last=|first=|date=2019-02-12|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref> the division works under one Deputy Commissioner.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/print-news/7856|title=DMP's counterterrorism unit likely from Feb -The Asian Age|last=|first=|date=2016-01-01|work=The Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/news/11220/dmps-counter-terrorism-unit-headed-by-monirul|title=DMP's counter-terrorism unit headed by Monirul|last=|first=|date=2016-02-18|work=The Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> He is assisted by two Additional Deputy Commissioners. They supervise four teams, namely:\n\n# Social Media Monitoring Team; \n# Website & E-mail Crime Team;\n# Digital Forencsic Team and \n# Mobile Finance Service.\n\nEach of these teams are led by one Assistant Commissioner. The total strength sanctioned for this division is very limited and is only 100.\n\n== Services ==\nThe Cyber Division services by its Help Desk, over hotline number, [[Email|e-mail]], Hello CT [[App store|apps]] and different [[Social media|social media platforms]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.govserv.org/BD/Dhaka/1719582295014901/Cyber-Security-%26-Crime-Division%2C-CTTC%2C-DMP|title=CYBER SECURITY & CRIME DIVISION, CTTC, DMP|last=|first=|date=|website=GOVSERV|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dmpnews.org/\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7-\u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0-\u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0-\u099c\u09c7/|title=\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0\u0983 \u099c\u09c7\u09a8\u09c7 \u09a8\u09bf\u09a8 \u0995\u09b0\u09a3\u09c0\u09af\u09bc|last=|first=|date=2018-10-03|website=Dhaka Metropolitan Police|language=Bengali|trans-title=Sexual Harassment in Online: Lets Know What to do|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/special-news/Concerns-growing-over-sexual-harassment-of-girls-on-social-media%C2%A0/71670|title=Concerns growing over sexual harassment of girls on social media|last=Shithi|first=Wahida Zaman|date=2018-05-27|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jugantor.com/lifestyle/24820/%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BE|title=\u09ab\u09c7\u09b8\u09ac\u09c1\u0995 \u09b9\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u0995 \u09b9\u09b2\u09c7 \u09ab\u09cb\u09a8\u09c7 \u09aa\u09be\u09ac\u09c7\u09a8 \u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b8\u09b9\u09be\u09af\u09bc\u09a4\u09be|last=Alimuzzaman|first=|date=2018-03-06|work=Daily Jugantor|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka|trans-title=Now get help from Police with your hacked Facebook ID}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.banglatribune.com/lifestyle/news/203687/%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8|title=\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09b9\u09b2\u09c7 \u09af\u09be \u0995\u09b0\u09ac\u09c7\u09a8|last=Ovee|first=Saddif|date=2017-05-04|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka|trans-title=Your first step after being harassed online.}}</ref>\n\n== Help desk ==\nThe Help Desk of Cyber Division is a unique innovation for instantly helping the cyber victims of Dhaka Metropolitan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.deshebideshe.com/news/details/56626|title=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 \u09a6\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09c7\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa \u09a1\u09c7\u09b8\u09cd\u0995|website=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 \u09a6\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09c7\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa \u09a1\u09c7\u09b8\u09cd\u0995 -Deshebideshe|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/bn/%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A7%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%A7%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80/a-19162022|title=\u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6\u09c7 \u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7\u09c7\u09b0 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a7\u09be\u09a8 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09a8\u09be\u09b0\u09c0 {{!}} DW {{!}} 04.04.2016|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|website=DW.COM|language=bn-BD|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/it-world/41217/\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0-\u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7--\u098f\u0995-\u09ac\u099b\u09b0\u09c7-\u09ea\u09e6-\u09b9\u09be\u099c\u09be\u09b0-\u0985\u09ad\u09bf\u09af\u09cb\u0997|title=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 : \u098f\u0995 \u09ac\u099b\u09b0\u09c7 \u09ea\u09e6 \u09b9\u09be\u099c\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09ad\u09bf\u09af\u09cb\u0997|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref> Each month on an average it serves more than 250 victims.\n\n== Forencsics Lab ==\nCyber Security & Crime Division has a state of art forensics lab which only provides forensics opinion for internal cases.\n\n== Awards ==\nIn 2017 one of the ADC Md Najmul Islam was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bd-pratidin.com/national/2018/01/08/295816|title=\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09c1\u09b0\u09b8\u09cd\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u09af\u09be\u09b0\u09be {{!}} \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8|website=Bangladesh Pratidin|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn 12 December 2018 this Division was awarded with [[Digital Bangladesh Award]] 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/post/357841/Walton-receives-digital-Bangladesh-award|title=Walton receives digital Bangladesh award|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn Police Week 2019 DC Md Alimuzzaman was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service) and ADC A F M Al Kibria, AC Sayed Nasirullah & Ishtiaque Ahmed were awarded with President Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/last-page/139166/\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6-\u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9\u09c7-\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09a6\u0995-\u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8-\u09e9\u09ea\u09ef-\u099c\u09a8|title=\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6 \u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9\u09c7 \u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09a6\u0995 \u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8 \u09e9\u09ea\u09ef \u099c\u09a8|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn Police Week 2020 SP Mishuk Chakma, AC Dhruba Joetirmoya Gope and Inspector Md Rafiqul Islam was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/last-page/263313/\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6-\u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9-\u09b6\u09c1\u09b0\u09c1-\u0986\u099c-\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8-\u09e7\u09e7\u09ee-\u099c\u09a8|title=\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6 \u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9 \u09b6\u09c1\u09b0\u09c1 \u0986\u099c: \u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8 \u09e7\u09e7\u09ee \u099c\u09a8|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!No\n!Name\n!Rank\n!Award\n!Year\n|-\n|1\n|Md Najmul Islam\n|ADC\n|BPM (Service)\n|2017\n|-\n|2\n|Cyber Security & Crime Division\n|\n|[[Digital Bangladesh Award]]\n|2018\n|-\n|3\n|Md Alimuzzaman\n|DC\n|BPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|4\n|A F M Al Kibria\n|ADC\n|PPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|5\n|Syed Nasirullah\n|AC\n|PPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|6\n|Ishtiaque Ahmed\n|AC\n|PPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|7\n|Mishuk Chakma\n|SP\n|BPM (Service)\n|2019\n|-\n|8\n|Dhruba Joetirmoya Gope\n|AC\n|BPM (Service)\n|2019\n|-\n|9\n|Md Rafiqul Islam\n|Inspector\n|BPM (Service)\n|2019\n|}\n\n== External Links ==\n\n* [https://www.cttcdmp.gov.bd/cyber Website of this Division]\n* [https://www.facebook.com/cyberctdmp/ Facebook Page of the Dvision]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Bangladesh Police]]\n[[Category:Computer security organizations]]\n[[Category:Law enforcement agencies of Bangladesh]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Branch of Bangladesh Police}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox law enforcement agency\n|agencyname     = Cyber Security & Crime Division \n|police         = Yes\n|headquarters   = 36 Minto Road, Ramna, [[Dhaka]] 1217\n|parentagency   = [[Dhaka Metropolitan Police]]\n|country        = Bangladesh\n|chief1name     = A F M Al Kibria\n|chief1position = Deputy Commissioner\n|employees      = 100\n|formedmonthday = 3 May\n|formedyear     = 2016\n|website        = {{URL|cttcdmp.gov.bd}}\n}}The '''Cyber Security & Crime Division''', more commonly known as the Cyber Crime Unit,<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/news/11220/dmps-counter-terrorism-unit-headed-by-monirul|title=DMP's counter-terrorism unit headed by Monirul|last=|first=|date=2016-02-18|work=Daily Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.observerbd.com/details.php?id=75128|title=DMP set to purchase 15 types of \u2018cyber arms\u2019|last=|first=|date=2017-05-24|work=The Daily Observer|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/bangladesh-news/those-spreading-rape-victims-photos-on-social-media-to-face-action-dmp/43065|title=Those spreading rape victims\u2019 photos on social media to face action: DMP|last=|first=|date=2017-05-20|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://en.banglatribune.com/others/news/43701/Investigation-into-Gulistan%E2%80%99s-bomb-underway-DMP|title=Investigation into Gulistan\u2019s bomb underway: DMP chief|last=|first=|date=2019-04-30|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> is a branch of [[Bangladesh Police]] which is operated under the [[Counter Terrorism and Transnational Crime]] of [[Dhaka Metropolitan Police]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/backpage/cybercrime-the-rise-1579035|title=Cybercrime on the rise|last=Islam, Jamil Khan|first=Shariful, Mohammad|date=2018-05-21|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/crime/2017/10/01/militants-secured-apps-dodge-cops|title=Militants using secured messaging apps to dodge cops|last=Mahmud, Rahman Rabbi|first=Tarek, Arifur|date=2017-10-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dmp.gov.bd/counter-terrorism/|title=Counter Terrorism|last=|first=|date=2018-12-01|website=Dhaka Metropolitan Police|location=Dhaka|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref> The main function of this division is to patrol, prevent, detect and investigate [[Cyberterrorism|cyber-terrorism]] and [[Cybercrime|cyber-crime]] in [[Dhaka|Dhaka Metropolitan]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/backpage/cybercrime-the-rise-1579035|title=Cybercrime on the rise|last=Islam, Jamil Khan|first=Shariful, Mohammad|date=2018-05-18|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/special-news/Concerns-growing-over-sexual-harassment-of-girls-on-social-media%C2%A0/71670|title=Concerns growing over sexual harassment of girls on social media|last=Shithi|first=Wahida Zaman|date=2018-05-27|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/showtime/2019/02/12/miss-world-bangladesh-2017-jessia-files-complaint-over-cyberbullying|title=Miss World Bangladesh 2017 Jessia files complaint over cyberbullying|last=|first=|date=2019-02-12|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/01/rise-in-cybercrime-worries-women|title=Rise in cybercrime worries women|last=|first=|date=2019-04-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/21/over-900-cases-related-to-cybercrimes-filed-in-2018|title=Over 900 cases related to cybercrimes filed in 2018|last=Islam Tipu|first=Md Sanul|date=2019-04-21|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/@pathao_ltd/cyber-security-crime-division-cttc-dmps-report-regarding-pathao-44a7e8db4fee|title=Cyber Security & Crime Division, CTTC, DMP\u2019s Report Regarding Pathao|last=|first=|date=2018-11-13|website=Medium|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-13}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\nThis division commenced its operation on 3 May 2016.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/114536/DMP-launches-counterterrorism-unit|title=DMP launches counter-terrorism unit|last=|first=|date=2016-02-16|work=Daily Sun|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/print-news/7856|title=DMP's counterterrorism unit likely from Feb -The Asian Age|last=|first=|date=2016-01-01|work=Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.clickittefaq.com/dmps-special-counter-terrorism-unit-to-start-functioning-in-february/|title=DMP\u2019s special counter terrorism unit to start functioning in February|last=|first=|date=2016-02-15|work=Ittefaq|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> Amidst the rise of [[Cybercrime|cyber crimes]] and [[Cyberbullying|cyber bullying]] in [[Bangladesh]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/post/194198|title=Cybercrimes escalate worries to female internet users|last=|first=|date=2019-04-02|work=The Independent BD|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/printversion/details/380753/2019/03/28/40-cases-filed-with-DMP-every-day|title=40 cases filed with DMP every day|last=Salman|first=Md Solaiman|date=2019-03-19|work=Daily Sun|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/cybersecurity/2019/04/01/rise-in-cybercrime-worries-women|title=Rise in cybercrime worries women|last=|first=|date=2019-04-01|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://en.banglatribune.com/tech-and-gadget/news/35788/Cyber-crime-committed-every-twenty-seconds|title=Cyber-crime committed every twenty seconds|last=Sarwar|first=Dipu|date=2019-03-25|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref> the policy makers took initiative to launch this dedicated Cyber Crime Division for Dhaka Metropolitan that will address digital crimes including [[Cyberbullying|online harassment]], [[Security hacker|hacking]], [[Internet fraud|Financial Fraud Crime]] and many more.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.observerbd.com/details.php?id=75128|title=DMP set to purchase 15 types of \u2018cyber arms\u2019|last=|first=|date=2017-05-24|work=The Daily Observer|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.clickittefaq.com/dmps-special-counter-terrorism-unit-to-start-functioning-in-february/|title=DMP\u2019s special counter terrorism unit to start functioning in February|last=|first=|date=2016-01-15|work=Ittefaq|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref>\n\n== Vision ==\nProtecting the [[netizen]]s of Dhaka Metropolitan by preventing cyber crime.\n\n== Mission ==\n<mapframe latitude=\"23.744\" longitude=\"90.404\" zoom=\"15\" width=\"263\" height=\"100\" align=\"right\" />[[File:Cyber Crime Unit, CTTC, DMP.jpg|thumb|''Cyber Division Help Desk''|alt=|262x262px]]\nKeeping the netizens of Dhaka Metropolitan safe and secured by investigating cyber incidents; monitoring social media sites, blogs and by raising public awareness.\n\n== Organization ==\nHeadquartered in 36 Minto Road, Ramna, [[Dhaka]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/showtime/2019/02/12/miss-world-bangladesh-2017-jessia-files-complaint-over-cyberbullying|title=Miss World Bangladesh 2017 Jessia files complaint over cyberbullying|last=|first=|date=2019-02-12|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref> the division works under one Deputy Commissioner.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/print-news/7856|title=DMP's counterterrorism unit likely from Feb -The Asian Age|last=|first=|date=2016-01-01|work=The Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailyasianage.com/news/11220/dmps-counter-terrorism-unit-headed-by-monirul|title=DMP's counter-terrorism unit headed by Monirul|last=|first=|date=2016-02-18|work=The Asian Age|access-date=2019-08-12|location=Dhaka}}</ref> He is assisted by two Additional Deputy Commissioners. They supervise four teams, namely:\n\n# Social Media Monitoring Team; \n# Website & E-mail Crime Team;\n# Digital Forencsic Team and \n# Mobile Finance Service.\n\nEach of these teams are led by one Assistant Commissioner. The total strength sanctioned for this division is very limited and is only 100.\n\n== Services ==\nThe Cyber Division services by its Help Desk, over hotline number, [[Email|e-mail]], Hello CT [[App store|apps]] and different [[Social media|social media platforms]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.govserv.org/BD/Dhaka/1719582295014901/Cyber-Security-%26-Crime-Division%2C-CTTC%2C-DMP|title=CYBER SECURITY & CRIME DIVISION, CTTC, DMP|last=|first=|date=|website=GOVSERV|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dmpnews.org/\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7-\u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0-\u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0-\u099c\u09c7/|title=\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0\u0983 \u099c\u09c7\u09a8\u09c7 \u09a8\u09bf\u09a8 \u0995\u09b0\u09a3\u09c0\u09af\u09bc|last=|first=|date=2018-10-03|website=Dhaka Metropolitan Police|language=Bengali|trans-title=Sexual Harassment in Online: Lets Know What to do|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://old.unb.com.bd/special-news/Concerns-growing-over-sexual-harassment-of-girls-on-social-media%C2%A0/71670|title=Concerns growing over sexual harassment of girls on social media|last=Shithi|first=Wahida Zaman|date=2018-05-27|work=United News of Bangladesh|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jugantor.com/lifestyle/24820/%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BE|title=\u09ab\u09c7\u09b8\u09ac\u09c1\u0995 \u09b9\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u0995 \u09b9\u09b2\u09c7 \u09ab\u09cb\u09a8\u09c7 \u09aa\u09be\u09ac\u09c7\u09a8 \u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b8\u09b9\u09be\u09af\u09bc\u09a4\u09be|last=Alimuzzaman|first=|date=2018-03-06|work=Daily Jugantor|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka|trans-title=Now get help from Police with your hacked Facebook ID}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.banglatribune.com/lifestyle/news/203687/%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A7%9F%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8|title=\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09af\u09bc\u09b0\u09be\u09a8\u09bf\u09b0 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09b9\u09b2\u09c7 \u09af\u09be \u0995\u09b0\u09ac\u09c7\u09a8|last=Ovee|first=Saddif|date=2017-05-04|work=Bangla Tribune|access-date=2019-08-13|location=Dhaka|trans-title=Your first step after being harassed online.}}</ref>\n\n== Help desk ==\nThe Help Desk of Cyber Division is a unique innovation for instantly helping the cyber victims of Dhaka Metropolitan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.deshebideshe.com/news/details/56626|title=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 \u09a6\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09c7\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa \u09a1\u09c7\u09b8\u09cd\u0995|website=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 \u09a6\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u09b9\u09c7\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa \u09a1\u09c7\u09b8\u09cd\u0995 -Deshebideshe|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/bn/%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A7%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%A7%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80/a-19162022|title=\u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6\u09c7 \u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7\u09c7\u09b0 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a7\u09be\u09a8 \u09b6\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09a8\u09be\u09b0\u09c0 {{!}} DW {{!}} 04.04.2016|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|website=DW.COM|language=bn-BD|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/it-world/41217/\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0-\u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7--\u098f\u0995-\u09ac\u099b\u09b0\u09c7-\u09ea\u09e6-\u09b9\u09be\u099c\u09be\u09b0-\u0985\u09ad\u09bf\u09af\u09cb\u0997|title=\u09b8\u09be\u0987\u09ac\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09aa\u09b0\u09be\u09a7 : \u098f\u0995 \u09ac\u099b\u09b0\u09c7 \u09ea\u09e6 \u09b9\u09be\u099c\u09be\u09b0 \u0985\u09ad\u09bf\u09af\u09cb\u0997|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref> Each month on an average it serves more than 250 victims.\n\n== Forencsics Lab ==\nCyber Security & Crime Division has a state of art forensics lab which only provides forensics opinion for internal cases.\n\n== Awards ==\nIn 2017 one of the ADC [[Md Najmul Islam]] was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bd-pratidin.com/national/2018/01/08/295816|title=\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09c1\u09b0\u09b8\u09cd\u0995\u09be\u09b0 \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u09af\u09be\u09b0\u09be {{!}} \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8|website=Bangladesh Pratidin|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn 12 December 2018 this Division was awarded with [[Digital Bangladesh Award]] 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daily-sun.com/post/357841/Walton-receives-digital-Bangladesh-award|title=Walton receives digital Bangladesh award|website=Daily Sun|language=en|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn Police Week 2019 DC Md Alimuzzaman was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service) and ADC A F M Al Kibria, AC Sayed Nasirullah & Ishtiaque Ahmed were awarded with President Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/last-page/139166/\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6-\u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9\u09c7-\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09a6\u0995-\u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8-\u09e9\u09ea\u09ef-\u099c\u09a8|title=\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6 \u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9\u09c7 \u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09a6\u0995 \u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8 \u09e9\u09ea\u09ef \u099c\u09a8|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\nOn Police Week 2020 SP Mishuk Chakma, AC Dhruba Joetirmoya Gope and Inspector Md Rafiqul Islam was awarded with Bangladesh Police Medal (service).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jugantor.com/todays-paper/last-page/263313/\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6-\u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9-\u09b6\u09c1\u09b0\u09c1-\u0986\u099c-\u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae-\u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8-\u09e7\u09e7\u09ee-\u099c\u09a8|title=\u09aa\u09c1\u09b2\u09bf\u09b6 \u09b8\u09aa\u09cd\u09a4\u09be\u09b9 \u09b6\u09c1\u09b0\u09c1 \u0986\u099c: \u09ac\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09bf\u09aa\u09bf\u098f\u09ae \u09aa\u09be\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u09c7\u09a8 \u09e7\u09e7\u09ee \u099c\u09a8|website=Jugantor|access-date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!No\n!Name\n!Rank\n!Award\n!Year\n|-\n|1\n|Md Najmul Islam\n|ADC\n|BPM (Service)\n|2017\n|-\n|2\n|Cyber Security & Crime Division\n|\n|[[Digital Bangladesh Award]]\n|2018\n|-\n|3\n|Md Alimuzzaman\n|DC\n|BPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|4\n|A F M Al Kibria\n|ADC\n|PPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|5\n|Syed Nasirullah\n|AC\n|PPM (Service)\n|2018\n|-\n|6\n|Ishtiaque Ahmed\n|AC\n|PPM (Service)\n